skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: minnesota meals
des:
Imagine yourself in the great state of Minnesota. You are very hungry after your trip up north and don't want to have to think about what to make for dinner. This skill is your lifesaver.

To enable the skill: Say "Alexa, enable Minnesota Meals" or search for "Minnesota Meals" in the Alexa mobile app or at Amazon.com. Click the enable button on the Minnesota Meals skills page.

To get started: Say "Alexa, ask Minnesota Meals what's for supper?" or "Alexa, ask Minnesota Meals what to make?"

Now you can eat in style, like a true Minnesotan would!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
